  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large pot over medium heat and sear the pork lardons until crispy.",
    "Remove the lardons and set aside, then sauté the onion and garlic in the rendered fat until translucent.",
    "Add the diced tofu to the pot and cook until lightly browned on all sides.",
    "Stir in the smoked paprika and cook for 30 seconds to release its aroma.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk, soy sauce, and fish sauce, stirring to combine.",
    "Return the crisped pork lardons to the pot, bring the mixture to a simmer, and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper, then garnish with fresh cilantro before serving.",
    "Divide the stew into meal prep containers for a convenient weeknight dinner."
